    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-07-03T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-07-03T13:00:00-05:00" n="186"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d186">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">462.00R296/4286: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Portugal</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Magruder</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-03T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 3, 1931—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>14. I have noted with appreciation that the Portuguese Government has decided
                    spontaneously to postpone for a year the collection of the <pb facs="0342"
                        n="228" xml:id="pg_228"/> German reparations due to Portugal and that this
                    action was notified in a statement relating to the budget for the fiscal year
                    1931–32. It is most encouraging to this Government to see that the Portuguese
                    Government is taking steps which are so fully in harmony with the President’s
                    proposal of June 20, 1931. The prompt and effective cooperation thus given by
                    the Portuguese Government toward relief and the re-establishment of economic
                    stability and prosperity in the world is most gratifying to this Government.</p>
                <p>Unless you perceive some reason for not doing so, please transmit the above to
                    the Minister for Foreign Affairs. Cable Department report of delivery.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Castle</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
